headline: Construction underway on $53M Milk-Bone plant renovation in Buffalo
summary: Work has begun on a $53 million renovation of the J.M. Smucker Co.’s Milk-Bone manufacturing facility located in Buffalo’s East Side. headline: SJM Q2 Deep Dive: Flat Sales, Margin Pressures, and Coffee Tariff Headwinds
summary: Packaged foods company J.M Smucker (NYSE:SJM) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales were flat year on year at $2.11 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.90 per share was 1.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
